<br>
ok... once you are whatever faction you want to be with Kromriff and kromzek, its now time to raise King Tormaxx faction... can be done in a number of ways... first one being... collect more dorf heads... save them till you have a nice collection... then, make your way to the bank... (dont post back asking where the bank is... go explore...Pollos something another is his name).. in the area of the bank, is either one of 2 giants, depending on your luck.. a Kromriff Military something or another.. or Captain Bvellos... Captain Bvellos is the one you seek, grasshoppa... hand in 4 dorf heads a pop to him, untill yer out of heads, or just feel like checking faction...<br>
<br>
by turning heads into Bvellos, you recieve King Tormaxx faction, as well as Kromriff and Kromzek.<br>
<br>
now, for the Paws that were mentioned, they are refering to ice kobold paws in Velks Lab... turn in 4 at a time to Captain Bvellos, and you recieve a trivial reward, plus kromriff, Kromzek, and King Tormaxx faction increases.<br>
<br>
to check your tormaxx faction, run out of the side door of the bank, and down the hall, till you see an ice bridge.. its small, but you should notice it. on the left, in the alcove, there should be about 3 giants, unless someone is pulling them.. the one in the back, should be on Tormaxx faction... target him, and con him... im not listing names, because it can be one of a few mobs in that spot.. best bet, is to try to target untill you get 3 different mobs, and have conned all of them.<br>
<br>
another way to raise factions, is to go to <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.everquest.allakhazam.com">www.everquest.allakhazam.com</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END-->  go to quests, look it up by faction.. there are a few that will raise tormax factions listed there.<br>
<br>
<br>
hope this has helped out some.. <p>Ianwen <br>
